* Convert from ClientLogin to "two-legged" OAuth.
  http://www.google.com/support/a/bin/answer.py?answer=61017&hl=en

* Support for additional attributes such as IM handles.

* Support for searching for contacts by attribute.

* Support for batch operations.

* Support deletion of attributes:
	contact.name.delete(:additionalName)
	-or-
	contact.name.additionalName.remove
